From Subject Acta Sanctorum in English Does anyone know whether the Acta Sanctorum the huge multi volume collection of Roman Catholic hagiography produced by the Bollandists has ever been translated into English I'm working on the Vita Dympnae and would love to be able to check my own translation against somebody else' Email replies preferred unless this query turns out to be of general Liz Broadwell Department of English Ad majorem Dei The University of Pennsylvania